{"arkId":"cl010109245","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010109245","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Tabati\u00e8re : micro-mosa\u00efque au chien et au chat","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Tabati\u00e8re : micro-mosa\u00efque au chien et au chat"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Le Directoire (1795-1799) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine-\u003EP\u00e9riode R\u00e9volutionnaire (1792-1799))\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1795 - 1797","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 555 - Biennais, Vitrine table","room":"Salle 555, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1795,"endYear":1797,"imprecision":"","text":"Fin du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Montauban, Pierre-Andr\u00e9","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"marque (estampilles, poin\u00e7ons...)","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 2131","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"accessoire personnel, bo\u00eete, \u00e9tui ; tabati\u00e8re","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Tabati\u00e8re de forme rectangulaire en or guilloch\u00e9 et \u00e9maill\u00e9, avec angles arrondis. Les panneaux, \u00e0 fond d\u0027or, sont guilloch\u00e9s d\u0027ondes et encadr\u00e9s de filets d\u0027\u00e9mail bleu roi translucide et de bordures d\u0027or sabl\u00e9. Les pilastres de la b\u00e2te sont cannel\u00e9s et \u00e9maill\u00e9s de m\u00eame.\r\nUne micro-mosa\u00efque polychrome de pierres dures est contenue dans le couvercle mont\u00e9 \u00e0 charni\u00e8re : elle a pour sujet la rencontre d\u0027un chien braque et d\u0027un chat, sur un fond de paysage verdoyant.\r\nLa mosa\u00efque a d\u00fb \u00eatre ex\u00e9cut\u00e9e vers 1800 \u00e0 Rome, o\u00f9 travaillaient des sp\u00e9cialistes comme Giacomo Raffaelli et les Barberi.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; poin\u00e7on \u00e0 la t\u00eate d\u0027enfant, 2e titre 1795-1797 (fond bo\u00eete, revers couvercle, revers bo\u00eete)\r ; poin\u00e7on de petite garantie (t\u00eate d\u0027aigle), Paris depuis 1838 (gorge, c\u00f4t\u00e9 droit)\r ; poin\u00e7on de petite garantie (t\u00eate de coq), Paris 1798-1809 (gorge, c\u00f4t\u00e9 droit)\r ; poin\u00e7on du ma\u00eetre Pierre-Andr\u00e9 Montauban (fond bo\u00eete, revers couvercle, revers bo\u00eete)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"1,9","displayDimension":"1,9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"8,4","displayDimension":"8,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"6,5","displayDimension":"6,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau\/Technique : Or, \u00e9mail, micro-mosa\u00efque de pierres dures\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)\r\nTechnique : micro-mosa\u00efque (techniques pierre\/ciment\/pl\u00e2tre\/cire-\u003Emosa\u00efque)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Philippe Lenoir ; legs M. et Mme Philippe Lenoir, 1874","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme Lenoir, Marie-Aspasie","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. Lenoir, Philippe Balthazard Marin","note